block(href='/hha') Go To Application Packet Form    .col-md-6.col-xl-4      .card        .card-body          h4.mt-0.header-title Spiritual Counselor (SC)          p.card-text is a type of counseling that focuses on a person's spiritual side. ... Some people might also seek out the guidance of spiritual counselors when they need help solving other problems in their lives, based on their spiritual beliefs.          a.btn.btn-info.waves-effect.waves-light.btn-block(href='/sc') Go To Application Packet Form    .col-md-6.col-xl-2.hide  // end row